            <form>
               <orth>buarach</orth>
            </form>
            <def>cow fetter tying the hind legs together when milking.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="CattleandSheep_SouthBragarDMacPhailcattle-d0e342">
            <form>
               <orth>spearrach</orth>
            </form>
            <def>a tether tying the fore and hind legs to prevent jumping over dykes and fences.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="CattleandSheep_SouthBragarDMacPhailcattle-d0e351">
            <form>
               <orth>stroinan</orth>
            </form>
            <def>spiked instrument to prevent the calf sucking its mother.</def>
         </entry>
